messages.messageBody:
Can you put in the edits that some authors have submitted? I don't see the edits that I sent to you. They're mostly just corrections for misspellings. But I'm embarassed to see my misspellings up there for all to see. <embarassed smile> :)

By the way, how do you spell "misspellings"?

Nina
